Welcome to FUSION Live Venice Nightclub!
DAILY EVENTS
Dear Guests, Friends, and Acquaintances,
We will be closing this Wednesday, March 19. likely for about a week, until the new management is ready to take over. This beautiful establishment is in urgent need of a fresh start, and we are determined to give it the care and attention it deserves.
If you would like to be part of this exciting new chapter—whether as a waiter, chef, bartender, or in any other capacity—we would love to hear from you! Please reach out to us at **
fusion.venice@gmail.com
**.
Thank you all for your support, and let’s come together to reinvent and revitalize our beloved Party House!
With gratitude,
Adding things everyday ...
